Description: 
v4l2codecs: Update bit_size and data_byte_offset based on
 updated docs

From discussion whilst upstreaming the Raspberry Pi HEVC decoder,
the bit_size and data_byte_offset definitions have been clarified.
They haven't been used by drivers until now.

Update the usage to match the new documentation.
 .
 gst-plugins-bad1.0 (1.26.2-3) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   * d/patches: 0001-h266parser-Fix-overflow-when-parsing-subpic_level_in.patch
     - Fix CVE-2025-6663 (Closes: #1108973)
       Fix overflow when parsing subpic_level_info in H.266 parser
Author: Marc Leeman <marc.leeman@gmail.com>
Bug-Debian: https://bugs.debian.org/1108973

